{"type": "article", "id": 21124, "title": "Patricia Urquiola 扶手椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-22T07:30:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110819GPvOcdDSJ23ZoxAT.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t西班牙建筑师 Patricia Urquiola 为意大利品牌 very wood 带去了两把扶手椅。都使用了可弯曲的橡木做结构，靠背和座位装有软垫。其中一把带白色布料的更接近传统的扶手椅，扶手和靠背是一个连贯的圆弧，而另一把椅子只有靠背装上了软垫，暴露出更多交叉的曲线结构，更适合户外。这两把扶手椅都有浓厚的欧洲风格。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110817O0vKzaRc4IQ1WrJX.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"542\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66259169\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110818OWnsg9C3f6UHVjcS.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"542\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66259169\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110818CiDJ3s9jR7YInm5k.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"734\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.89731051\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110819k14tSCUZVbLjJYEP.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"970\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.18581907\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n"}